<a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-UA4hWegucz8/VrBV8H63Q-I/AAAAAAAAVvk/0sTm9zdwUjU/s1600/Theri%2BFirst%2BLook.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em;"><img border="0" height="400" src="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-UA4hWegucz8/VrBV8H63Q-I/AAAAAAAAVvk/0sTm9zdwUjU/s400/Theri%2BFirst%2BLook.jpg" width="255" /></a><br />
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<b>Casting: </b>Vijay, Samantha, Amy Jackson</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<br /></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<b>Director: </b>Atlee Kumar</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<br /></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<b>Music By: </b>GV Prakash Kumar</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<br /></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<b>Producer: </b>Kalaipuli S Thanu</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<br /></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<b>Budget: </b>1 Billion<b> </b>INR</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<br /></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<b>Release Date: </b>April 2016</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<br /></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
&nbsp;Theri is an upcoming Tamil film directed by Raja Rani fame Atlee Kumar. It is 59th film for Vijay. Samantha is fairing up with Vijay for the 2nd time after a Kaththi which is a Blockbuster of 2014 which is directed by AR Murugadoss. Vijay will be seen as a Police officer in this film.</div>
<span style="font-size: large;"><b><br /></b></span>
